{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<i>","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概述","title":"概述","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>HTML 元素 <code>&lt;i&gt;</code></strong> 用于表现因某些原因需要区分普通文本的一系列文本。例如技术术语、外文短语或是小说中人物的思想活动等，它的内容通常以斜体显示。</p>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">Content catergories</a></dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Flow content</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>, palpable content.</li>\n <li><dfn>允许量</dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>标签忽略</dfn> 不允许，开始标签和结束标签都不能省略。</li>\n <li><dfn>Permitted parent elements</dfn> Any element that accepts <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>DOM interface</dfn> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a> Up to Gecko 1.9.2 (Firefox 4) inclusive, Firefox implements the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code></a> interface for this element.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>该元素只包含 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">全局属性</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>The Latin phrase <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>i</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>latin<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Veni, vidi, vici<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>i</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> is often\nmentioned in music, art, and literature<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result","title":"效果","isH3":true,"content":"<p>The Latin phrase <em>Veni, vidi, vici</em> is often mentioned in music, art, and literature</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"注释","title":"注释","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在较早版本的 HTML 技术参数声明中，<code>&lt;i&gt;</code> 标签只是一个用于将文本显示为斜体的表示性元素，很像 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/b\"><code>&lt;b&gt;</code></a> 标签被用来将文本显示为粗体。情况不再是这样了，因为这些标签现在定义了更多的语义而不只是排版外观。<code>&lt;i&gt;</code> 标签应表现一系列带有不同语义的文本，它的典型样式显示为斜体。这意味着浏览器通常任会将内容显示为斜体，但是，根据定义，不再是必须的。</p>\n\n<p>该元素只在没有更适合的语义元素表示时使用。例如：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a> 表示强调或重读。</li>\n <li>使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a> 表示重要性。</li>\n <li>使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/mark\"><code>&lt;mark&gt;</code></a> 表示相关性。</li>\n <li>使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a> 标记著作名，如一本书、剧本或是一首歌。</li>\n <li>使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code></a> 标记术语的定义实例。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>使用<strong>class</strong>属性用来识别为何使用该元素是一个很好的办法，这样的话，如果该表示以后需要改变，就可以有选择性地改变样式表。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"技术参数","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/text-level-semantics.html#the-i-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;i&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/text-level-semantics.html#the-i-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;i&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/present/graphics.html#h-15.2.1\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;b&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.i","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概述","id":"概述"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"注释","id":"注释"},{"text":"技术参数","id":"specifications"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"HTML 元素 <i> 用于表现因某些原因需要区分普通文本的一系列文本。例如技术术语、外文短语或是小说中人物的思想活动等，它的内容通常以斜体显示。","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<i>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<i>: The Idiomatic Text element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"i","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<i>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<i>: 慣用的なテキスト要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<i>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"i","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<i>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/i","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/element/i/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i","title":"<i>"}],"pageTitle":"<i> - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}